evidence.text: Plaintiffs fail to demonstrate a likelihood of success on the merits of their claims, their motion for the extraordinary remedy of preliminary injunctive relief must be denied.

extracted.value: The court denied Plaintiffs' motion for preliminary injunctive relief, finding they failed to demonstrate a likelihood of success on the merits of their claims.
